AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: encryption-provider-nodeLaunchConfiguration-b672362
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-0016572b","subnet-0b4f9fb1df1543b07","subnet-43f43a1e","subnet-c7d926bf","subnet-d7e7fe9c"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: encryption-provider-eksCluster-3c6a95d-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/encryption-provider-eksCluster-3c6a95d
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
